Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.39,0:00:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.20,0:00:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翌晨的陽光就快來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.40,0:00:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照進這間充滿煙蒂\N雜亂無章的屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.38,0:00:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why 聖母瑪利亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.48,0:00:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對溫柔感到飢渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.52,0:00:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.42,0:00:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼孤單的夜晚\N總是如此漫長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.17,0:00:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛仔褲下的膝蓋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.04,0:00:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被破碎的夢想打溼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.34,0:01:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著襯衫的胸部太過耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.35,0:01:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.41,0:01:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要敷衍我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.38,0:01:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止,我要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.25,0:01:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.72,0:01:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我話還沒說完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.95,0:01:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.32,0:01:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.50,0:01:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.13,0:01:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.70,0:02:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.07,0:02:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上荻老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.04,0:02:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳聽我說,這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.64,0:02:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.48,0:02:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#55 睡衣女孩突擊!\N一刻館愛情大混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.43,0:02:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.70,0:02:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那件事之後\N班導就盯得很緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.61,0:02:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且問題在於那個寡婦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.74,0:02:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.98,0:02:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底算是被壓得抬不起頭來?\N還是被管理?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.55,0:02:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們之間有種很奇怪的氣氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.59,0:02:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錯不了的,他們兩個一定有一腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.32,0:02:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要光靠氣氛就亂下評斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.03,0:03:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是八神,妳打算怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.13,0:03:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後天教學實習就要結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.17,0:03:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.57,0:03:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要放棄嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.64,0:03:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.10,0:03:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,怎麼都沒掃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.35,0:03:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會放棄呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.32,0:03:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年紀大有什麼了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.25,0:03:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我比她有魅力多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.56,0:03:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,那個寡婦\N跟我們班導好像蠻熟的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.83,0:03:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且感覺好像\N不是第一次來這個學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.37,0:03:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.88,0:03:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.15,0:03:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寡婦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.99,0:04:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是說音無響子嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.22,0:04:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師認識她嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.86,0:04:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,她是這裡的畢業生\N也是我的學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.93,0:04:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時她跟在這所學校\N教書的音無老師結婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.21,0:04:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟老師結婚?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.71,0:04:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是她自己倒追老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.18,0:04:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊,那不就跟我一樣囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.21,0:04:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她沒像妳那麼激烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.86,0:04:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼慢\N八神到底在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.43,0:04:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能在追著五代老師跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.03,0:04:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了,今天是星期六耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.73,0:04:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神好像蠻認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.81,0:04:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,那個寡婦也跟老師…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.98,0:05:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣她就沒有資格\N阻止我跟五代老師囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.96,0:05:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,妳在幹什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.46,0:05:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這樣大家要怎麼回去嘛\N八神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.19,0:05:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的鞋子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.53,0:05:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,我要去找她攤牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.88,0:05:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,好勁爆喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.88,0:05:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情蠻多的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.52,0:05:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊?真不敢相信\N因為男人的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.22,0:05:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的很遜耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.76,0:05:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三號月台,準急電車快進站了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.56,0:05:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請各位乘客退到白線後面\N以策安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.17,0:06:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八…八神…同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.14,0:06:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天星期天\N可以去老師家玩嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.35,0:06:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.79,0:06:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,對了,明天我奶奶病危…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.92,0:06:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師,你也拜託一下\N不要對我這麼警戒嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.90,0:06:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們也會一起去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.20,0:06:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.13,0:06:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去,你就不會怕了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.80,0:06:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是沒錯啦\N不是,我不是害怕啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.57,0:06:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就這麼敲定了\N打勾勾一言為定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.23,0:06:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.43,0:06:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下星期一\N教學實習終於要結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.46,0:06:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,是沒錯啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.74,0:07:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你捨不得八神嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.41,0:07:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼捨不捨得,我根本無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.84,0:07:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N我也沒什麼特別的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.48,0:07:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是那個女孩,知道這個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.79,0:07:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題就在這裡\N明天她也說要來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.04,0:07:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算教學實習結束了\N並不保證以後就不會見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.02,0:07:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.89,0:08:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.40,0:08:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.50,0:08:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次很謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.73,0:08:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.04,0:08:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你過來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.58,0:08:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人要來就先說一聲嘛\N我可以準備一下的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.25,0:08:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,這怎麼好意思…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.05,0:08:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像一對夫妻喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.12,0:08:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我猜想的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有夫妻的氣氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,不用妳費心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.36,0:08:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.73,0:08:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師是個單身漢\N一定什麼都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.30,0:08:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我已經買了很多東西來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.07,0:08:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真是體貼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.64,0:08:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.44,0:08:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.51,0:08:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真是超級積極派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.69,0:09:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是四谷,在此恭候各位多時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.53,0:09:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧,各位請坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.66,0:09:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛇叔叔今天好帥喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.37,0:09:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件是新的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.87,0:09:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,昨晚我死去的奶奶托夢給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.94,0:09:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我要穿白色的禮服\N迎接你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.34,0:09:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個廚房好髒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.90,0:09:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有同樣的咖啡杯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.07,0:09:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代這樣也無所謂吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.74,0:09:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.54,0:09:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛,居然話中帶刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.42,0:10:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣啦,蛇叔叔好討厭喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.59,0:10:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳那一大包是什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.76,0:10:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!打翻了打翻了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.36,0:10:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點擦一擦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.97,0:10:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我的也打翻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.30,0:10:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抹布,快拿抹布來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.84,0:10:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.34,0:10:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點擦啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.81,0:10:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒用…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.99,0:10:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.09,0:10:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.83,0:10:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.63,0:10:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真捨不得你們走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.06,0:11:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.46,0:11:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!妳要在這裡過夜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.63,0:11:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,不行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.97,0:11:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經跟家裡的人說\N要住在朋友家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.44,0:11:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今,回不去了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.98,0:11:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-妳給我回去!\N-不要!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.64,0:11:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把妳趕出去喔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.38,0:11:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有本事你就趕趕看啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.12,0:11:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是要這樣子才有意思嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.19,0:11:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.19,0:11:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣繼續下去的話\N只會讓別人誤會而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.73,0:11:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明明摸了我的胸部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.63,0:11:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.16,0:11:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸部?看來事情非比尋常喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.47,0:12:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在體育器材室摸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.30,0:12:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.94,0:12:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代開始慌亂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.04,0:12:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是個意外,意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.51,0:12:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,況且那是妳設計的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.74,0:12:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就很難說囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.61,0:12:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代是個大色狼\N一定是他故意去摸的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.82,0:12:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你們不要加油添醋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.76,0:12:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.10,0:12:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要罵那麼兇比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.80,0:12:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,我不能再縱容她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.53,0:12:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要好好教訓她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.64,0:12:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,妳給我聽清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.07,0:12:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是個高中生\N也要有點社會常識…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.02,0:12:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你摸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.68,0:12:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你摸了我的胸部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.49,0:12:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼好哭的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.62,0:12:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我嫁不出去了啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.09,0:13:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,八神…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.93,0:13:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.13,0:13:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,膽子真大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.21,0:13:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,快把衣服穿上,穿上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.52,0:13:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.63,0:13:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經換上了這種衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.92,0:14:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家圍著吃飯,吃起來真愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.72,0:14:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還邀請我一起來吃\N真是太高興了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.33,0:14:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有人邀請你來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.50,0:14:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且八神的炒青菜\N吃起來苦苦的真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.64,0:14:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有放木耳耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.51,0:14:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,這是炒焦的高麗菜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.78,0:14:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興喔,你那麼喜歡吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.31,0:14:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上我會做馬鈴薯燉肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.15,0:14:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.42,0:14:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就讓她住下來嘛,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.92,0:14:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.89,0:14:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,妳給我聽好\N吃完後就回去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.09,0:14:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我送妳去車站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我穿這個不能回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.80,0:14:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳就去換衣服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.13,0:14:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.07,0:14:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩到底在想什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.07,0:14:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算什麼事都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.34,0:14:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡過夜\N也要考慮到旁人的眼光吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.15,0:15:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之要賴到最後一班電車開走\N我一定要在這裡過夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.28,0:15:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不肯讓我住在\N五代老師的房裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.29,0:15:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候我就去住寡婦那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.56,0:15:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這剛好是個\N可以跟她談判的好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.79,0:15:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,吃得好飽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.43,0:15:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝招待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.47,0:15:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.50,0:15:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是爸爸的晚飯,拿去給他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.61,0:15:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.58,0:15:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我來幫你準備吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.88,0:15:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.43,0:15:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,請上床吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.10,0:15:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用顧慮我們,盡情享受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.04,0:15:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在胡說什麼\N不要開這種玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.47,0:16:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來來來,快來這裡,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.98,0:16:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進去吧,進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.98,0:16:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.98,0:16:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然叫我這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.85,0:16:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.19,0:16:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聊天也聊了,晚飯也吃了\N接下來當然只剩睡覺囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.49,0:16:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.03,0:16:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要回去就趁現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.96,0:16:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳以為這些人是在開玩笑\N那就大錯特錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.50,0:16:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,這些人是活在這世上的\N最沒常識的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.31,0:16:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.51,0:16:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就把我當成小孩,看不起我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.72,0:16:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.82,0:16:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是愛賭氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.49,0:16:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.33,0:16:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧,讓妳睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.16,0:16:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去睡四谷的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本人拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.04,0:17:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家有三個人已經擠不下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.11,0:17:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.78,0:17:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法,到我房間來睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.08,0:17:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,管理員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼辦法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.59,0:17:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個寡婦究竟爛到什麼程度啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.36,0:17:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太下流了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.93,0:17:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然若無其事的\N叫男人去她的房間睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.83,0:17:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,這樣好嗎?\N真的要讓我睡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.70,0:17:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.17,0:17:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,起來\N到我的房間去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.21,0:17:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.52,0:17:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就說清楚嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.59,0:17:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.19,0:18:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師,你要夢到我唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到她這麼容易就放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.75,0:18:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,給妳添麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.25,0:18:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.08,0:18:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是個好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.52,0:18:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要勸勸她\N不要再纏著五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.66,0:18:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這個女孩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.83,0:18:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來也不可能乖乖聽勸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.86,0:18:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.57,0:18:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我一直想找個機會\N跟妳好好聊一聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.47,0:18:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼叫我學姊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.51,0:18:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳是我們學校的\N畢業生不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.01,0:18:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是沒錯啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.49,0:19:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姊,我問妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.83,0:19:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳從高中時代\N胸部就那麼大了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.57,0:19:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,跟妳現在差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.27,0:19:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼妳是靠楚楚可憐\N才成功到手的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.84,0:19:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.81,0:19:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是聽班導說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.85,0:19:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姊,妳跟老師結婚了不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.18,0:19:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳能不能告訴我一些\N具體的成功祕訣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.35,0:19:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我當作以後的參考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.96,0:19:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,我先問妳\N妳是真的喜歡五代嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.69,0:19:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.60,0:19:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是閒閒沒事逗著他玩的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.34,0:19:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.37,0:19:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是一時意亂情迷嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.51,0:19:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.11,0:19:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人哪裡好啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.31,0:20:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不可以喜歡五代老師嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.95,0:20:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是不可以啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.69,0:20:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是我看到妳的所作所為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.12,0:20:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很奇怪嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.16,0:20:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一點超越了常軌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.53,0:20:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.00,0:20:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.40,0:20:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望有師生戀成功經驗的學姊\N能直接傳授我正確的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.08,0:20:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡覺吧,妳明天還要上學不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.57,0:21:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得不放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.11,0:21:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個八神不可能乖乖睡覺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.18,0:21:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.62,0:21:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姊,學姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.45,0:21:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要裝睡嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.26,0:21:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳一定是很喜歡五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.13,0:21:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這樣\N所以才會一直破壞我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.64,0:21:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼時候破壞你們了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.47,0:21:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不讓我睡在五代老師的房裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.61,0:21:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在胡說什麼啊\N我這是在幫妳耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.24,0:21:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是個高中生,可能還不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.92,0:21:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代也是個男人耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.85,0:21:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼,我還擔心得要命\N特地跑來看看的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.42,0:21:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好\N妳應該更加愛惜自己才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.63,0:21:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真傻,回去睡覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.67,0:22:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要說這種老掉牙的道理\N學姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.17,0:22:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說妳啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.07,0:22:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要從中阻撓?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.41,0:22:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是個管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.94,0:22:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓人在公寓裡\N亂搞男女關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.84,0:22:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連房客談戀愛\N妳都有義務管理嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.59,0:22:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就直接問了\N五代老師很喜歡學姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.19,0:22:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這又怎麼樣呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.76,0:22:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那學姊妳呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.13,0:22:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳喜歡五代老師嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.27,0:22:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼樣?\N妳也很喜歡他吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.94,0:22:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.75,0:22:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對他沒什麼感覺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.03,0:23:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.77,0:23:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.03,0:23:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點走吧,會遲到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.51,0:23:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們的感情不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.78,0:23:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.19,0:23:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起喔,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.66,0:23:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,等等我\N對不起嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.64,0:23:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,學生寫的感想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.34,0:23:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好照顧八神一輩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.41,0:23:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結婚的時候要請我喝喜酒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.75,0:23:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再說了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.95,0:23:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神的事已經結束了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.82,0:23:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.35,0:23:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『八神的決心!\N絕不放棄,因為這是初戀』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.62,0:24:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安,五代老師
